  <p><strong>Day CQ WCM Version Manager</strong> Control if, and how, versions are managed in your system:</p> 
  <ul> 
   <li><strong>Create Version on Activation</strong>, enabled in a standard installation</li> 
   <li><strong>Enable Purging</strong><br /> </li> 
   <li><strong>Purge Paths</strong>, the paths that a search action will search</li> 
   <li><strong>Implicit Versioning Paths</strong>, the paths where implicit versioning is active.<br /> </li> 
   <li><strong>Max Version Age</strong>, the maximum age (in days) of a version<br /> </li> 
